《孤岛危机2》受到了比较正面的评价。评论者称赞了游戏的图形设计和主角的纳米战斗服，批评了游戏的线性玩法，称其不如前作以及[[Crytek|Crytek]]广受好评的作品《[[孤岛惊魂_(游戏)|孤岛惊魂]]》。评分汇总网站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的评分分别为：PC版85.68%和86/100<ref name="GRPC" /><ref name="MCPC" />；Xbox 360版85.50%和84/100<ref name="GRX360" /><ref name="MCX360" />；PlayStation 3版85.21%和85/100<ref name="GRPS3" /><ref name="MCPS3" />。

[[官方Xbox杂志|官方Xbox杂志]]给予游戏9/10分，称游戏在线上“会遇到的一些最令人兴奋、满意的行动”，单人战役的庞大场面也给人留下了深刻印象<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/292287/news/crysis-2-review-9/10-in-oxm/ |title=Crysis 2 review - 9/10 in OXM |date=2011-03-07 |accessdate=2011-03-08 |publisher=CVG |archive-date=2011-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310044918/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/292287/news/crysis-2-review-9/10-in-oxm/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Gamereactor|Gamereactor]]给予游戏9/10分，指出“游戏设计了原始丛林和到处是断壁残垣的纽约这两种令人兴奋的场景对比”。另一方面，评论员批评了游戏的故事，称“游戏对话经常让人感到不当，人物表现平淡无趣，Crytek明显受到《[[半条命2|半条命2]]》的启发，尽管他们野心很大，但他们从未达到[[维尔福|维尔福]]的高度。”“这只是一个耻辱而不能被称为最好的动作游戏”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamereactor.eu/reviews/6760/Crysis+2/ |title=Crysis 2 review - 9/10 from Gamereactor |date=2011-03-16 |accessdate=2011-03-21 |archive-date=2011-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110320095624/http://www.gamereactor.eu/reviews/6760/Crysis+2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》认为游戏大量借鉴比游戏更为线性的《[[使命召唤|使命召唤]]》系列的枪械，称游戏为一场“被堵塞”的经历<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8398164/Crysis-2-review.html |title=Crysis 2 review |date=2011-03-22 |accessdate=2011-03-22 |publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |quote=''Crysis 2 borrows more from the Call of Duty school of shooters than it does from its predecessor(...)It's soon clear that playing as Alcatraz, Crysis 2's protagonist, is designed to be a cinematic, often scripted experience'' |archive-date=2011-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110325004240/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8398164/Crysis-2-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。报纸还批评了敌人的“残暴的”AI，“成问题”的声音和“平淡”的多人模式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8398164/Crysis-2-review.html |title=Crysis 2 review |date=2011-03-22 |accessdate=2011-03-22 |publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |quote=''But it's massively uninspiring stuff. If you haven't played any popular FPS title in the last five years, and you don't own any of them either, then ''Crysis 2''{{'}}s multiplayer mode is as good an FPS multiplayer to get into as any. But if you have, and you're already invested in another game, then this carbon copy'' |archive-date=2011-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110325004240/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8398164/Crysis-2-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

官方Xbox杂志对PlayStation 3版的评分为8/10，称游戏“技术过硬，视觉突出，充满新点子”“开发商Crytek将游戏的硬件要求推向顶峰，其在PS3上的首秀是一流的，”“它不只是看起来好，它是不同的，在[[使命召唤|使命召唤]]和[[荣誉勋章|荣誉勋章]]不断使用深卡其色的背景后，弯曲的尖塔和绿色城市空间融合的曼哈顿令人耳目一新。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/293334/news/crysis-2-review-8/10-in-official-playstation-mag/ |title=Crysis 2 review - 8/10 in Official PlayStation Mag |date=2011-03-14 |accessdate=2011-03-14 |publisher=CVG |archive-date=2011-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110316154417/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/293334/news/crysis-2-review-8/10-in-official-playstation-mag/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

和孤岛危机一代允许用户更改各种图形设置不同，《孤岛危机2》发布时提供的图形选项较少。但是，DX11和高级选项功能在1.8版中得到添加<ref>{{cite web |url=https://secure.mycrysis.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=40&t=28490 |title=Patch 1.8 now live |date=2011-05-25 |accessdate=2011-06-05 |publisher=[[Crytek|Crytek]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811081136/https://secure.mycrysis.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=40&t=28490 |archivedate=2011-08-11 }}</ref>，并与高清材质补丁一同发布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://secure.mycrysis.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=40&t=22276&start=1500|title=Crysis 2 DirectX 11 Patch Announced!|date=2011-04-08|accessdate=2011-06-05|publisher=[[Crytek|Crytek]]|quote=''We would like to announce that there will be a DX11 patch released for Crysis 2. We are working to get the best out of DX11. Patch 1.9.0.0 has been confirmed for release on June 27th, which will be required to make the High-Res Texture and DX11 packs work. The DX11 Ultra Upgrade Pack adds "hardware tessellation, parallax occlusion mapping, and several upgrades for shadows, water, particles, depth of field, and motion blur."''|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531055144/https://secure.mycrysis.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=40&t=22276&start=1500|archivedate=2012-05-31}}</ref>。高清材质补丁可以DX9或DX11模式下使用（显卡必须拥有768 MB或更大显存），但仅支持64位操作系统<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mycrysis.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=27&t=32062 |title=MyCrysis Forums - Crysis 2 PC Patch 1.9 FAQ + Known Issues |publisher=Mycrysis.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618075536/http://www.mycrysis.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=27&t=32062 |archivedate=2013-06-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mycrysis.com/sites/default/files/support/download/c2_dx11_ultra_upgrade.pdf |title=has moved! |publisher=Mycrysis.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514141853/http://www.mycrysis.com/sites/default/files/support/download/c2_dx11_ultra_upgrade.pdf |archivedate=2013-05-14 }}</ref>。

截至2011年6月30日，《孤岛危机2》全平台销量超过300万，低于《[[孤岛危机|孤岛危机]]》的PC销量<ref>{{cite web|url=http://investor.ea.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=594196|title=Electronic Arts Reports Q1 FY12 Financial Results (NASDAQ:ERTS)|date={{Date|2011-07-26|mdy}}|accessdate={{Date|2011-07-28|mdy}}|publisher=[[Electronic_Arts|Electronic Arts]]|archive-date=2011-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807213559/http://investor.ea.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=594196|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

